race.comment: FANCY GARTER (2) has her hoof on the till after finishing an improved second over 1300m at Goulburn. Placed here and will relish the drop in trip. Hard to hold out. SI SI MILANO (1) former Victorian gelding having her first start for the Kearney yard. Big drop in grade with the claim after disappointing when sixth over 1200m at Moe. Visors go on from the good gate. Top three prospect. GLOWING RAPIDS (4) win record hardly excites but a win looks imminent. Strong late when fourth over 1200m at Dubbo. Goes well here and is capable of taking this out. NOTLEANORMEAN (3) was in the money two starts back at Young but was unable to repeat the effort last time when seventh over 1200m at Dubbo. Gets the right set-up today.
